# Long-Term Vision

After Design Freeze, Decidera will evolve through multiple implementation phases.

Possible future phases include:

- Phase 0 — Bootstrap
- Phase 1 — Core Workspace
- Phase 2 — Forum Engine
- Phase 3 — Artifact Engine
- Phase 4 — Provider Integration
- Phase 5 — AI Capability
- Phase 6 — Ecosystem Expansion

These phases remain conceptual until the Design Book is finalized.

---

# Guiding Principles

The roadmap follows several principles.

- Design before implementation.
- Documentation before automation.
- Decisions before coding.
- Stable architecture before optimization.
- Evolution through documented changes.

---

